body_html: I am running into the same issue on 1.4.0-rc0 (compiled from source, bazel v0.7.0). At first I thought it was trying to load the model on a Raspberry Pi that caused this, but it looks like I cannot load the frozen model even on the very workstation it was created on. Any tips on how to deal with this?
